hispanic undergraduate business association stanford university updates constitution application huba is a student run organization that promotes exposure to career opportunities in the fields of investment science finance and entrepreneurship our associates are driven students from a broad range of disciplines at stanford university with the common vision of advancing latinos in the business world the goals of huba are as follows first to foster a genuine interest in the fields of finance investment and entrepreneurship second develop high caliber latino candidates for careers in business third to give back to the community as a whole through community service contact us huba
